HEADWORD: Phlegmonous
<hw>Phleg"mon*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>phlegmoneux</ets>.]</ety> <def>Having the nature or properties of
phlegmon; <as>as, <ex>phlegmonous</ex> pneumonia</as>.</def>
